Package src.user_data

Class User

java.lang.Object
src.user_data.User
Direct Known Subclasses:
Staff, Student
public abstract class User extends Object
The User class is an abstract class representing a user in the system.

A user has a unique identifier, name, password, email, role, and belongs to a specific faculty. This class serves as the base class for more specific user types, such as Staff, Student, and CampCommittee.
